Crazy lucky for this life we live and my little family!!! 2022 was great, 2023 is going to be better yet!!! Happy New Year everyone!

This man taught me so much. First of all he believed in me, took me under his wing and treated me like family. He welcomed my family into his home and unknowingly taught me how to be a good husband and eventually father while navigating this crazy life we live. He was a visionary, a doer, and most importantly above all he was a great husband, absolutely amazing father and a great friend. Words can’t explain how much Ken Block will be missed. I feel like the luckiest guy on earth each day I get to wake up next to my smokin hot, cool as hell, fun as can be, sassy as they come, badass wife!!! Love ya to death @jenn.arpin and thanks for having low enough standards that a guy like me gets to live this life with a girl like you!! Happy Valentine’s Day babe!! Ryder and I are the luckiest boys on earth to have you!!

“Children are a gift from the Lord; they are a reward from him” Psalm 127:3

We are thrilled to announce that Ryder is getting a baby SISTER this November! Thank you, Jesus, for entrusting us with this sweet baby girl!

Happy 70th birthday pops!!! Love you to death and couldn’t have dreamt of a better father to have in my life! Jen and I appreciate you so much and are so lucky that our kids have you in their lives helping influence and develop them! Hope it’s a perfect day for you and can’t wait to celebrate soon!!!
Our little man is 2 already!! Blows my mind how proud I am to be this little man’s dad! Happy Birthday Ryder, love you little buddy!!!

I am officially the luckiest man on earth!! Chloe Marie Arpin decided to come on her own schedule and surprised us a little early! Her mother is an absolute rock star and I am beyond grateful to have these two beautiful children and the world’s most amazing wife/mother to share this life with!! So in love already!
